20. Re1 Nf6 $1 21. Rec1 Ra6 $3 {Preparing to double on the a-file and
protecting c6.} 22. g3 (22. Ra1 Rxa1 23. Rxa1 Bxb4 $19) 22... Rea8 23. Kg2 Ra3
24. Qb2 Nd7 $1 25. Nd2 (25. Ne2 Ra2) 25... Nb6 $19 {...Nc4 is coming with a
