should have reacted with the thematic} 12. e4 $1 dxe4 13. Nxe4 Nxe4 14. Bxe4
O-O 15. Re1 Qf6 {though Black still has an acceptable position.}) 12... g4 ({
Black should have gone for} 12... Be6 $1 13. Re1 O-O-O $17 {when he can use
the hook on h3 to open the g-file.}) 13. e4 $1 $13 Bf4 14. Re1 Be6 15. exd5
