1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 ({We reach the position in the game via the move
order} 3. Nf3 d5 4. Nc3 Nbd7 5. cxd5 exd5 6. Bg5 h6 7. Bh4 Bb4 8. Nd2 c6 9. e3)
3... Bb4 4. Nf3 d5 5. cxd5 exd5 6. Bg5 h6 7. Bh4 Nbd7 8. e3 g5 9. Bg3 Ne4 10.
Nd2 Nxg3 11. hxg3 c6 12. Qc2 Kf8 $1 (12... Nb6 $1) (12... Nf6 $6 13. Nf3 $1 {
[%cal Gf3g5]}) 13. Bd3 Kg7 14. O-O-O Nf6 {With the king on the kingside, the
knight is needed on f6.} 15. Nf3 $6 Ng4 $15 16. Kb1 Bxc3 $3 $17 17. bxc3 Qe7 (
17... Qf6 $1 18. e4 dxe4 19. Bxe4 Be6 $17 {[%csl Rb1,Gg7]} (19... Re8 $17)) 18.
Rhe1 f5 $6 19. Re2 Rf8 20. Qb2 a5 21. Ne1 b5 22. Bc2 b4 23. cxb4 axb4 24. Bb3
Nf6 25. Rc2 Ne4 26. Nd3 Nc3+ 27. Rxc3 bxc3 28. Qxc3 Ba6 29. Qc5 Bxd3+ 30. Rxd3
Qxc5 31. dxc5 Ra5 32. Rc3 f4 33. gxf4 gxf4 34. exf4 Rxf4 35. f3 Kf6 36. g3 Rf5
37. f4 Rh5 38. a4 Rh2 39. Bc2 h5 40. Kc1 Ra8 41. Re3 Ra5 42. Rc3 Rh3 43. Kb2 h4
